do for her!

1351
01:26:54,930 --> 01:26:56,863
The man is crazy.

1352
01:26:57,325 --> 01:27:01,911
The stupid thing is that he didn't
see the bracelet had fallen off.

1353
01:27:01,912 --> 01:27:05,556
By leaving an empty box in my
jewelry drawer-

1354
01:27:05,557 --> 01:27:08,967
You made it appear that she
had boosted it.

1355
01:27:09,307 --> 01:27:11,494
She wasn't stupid:

1356
01:27:11,882 --> 01:27:14,960
